caption:
The most successful people I've met:

1. Passionately exalt the Glass Fronts from Cabinets
2. Revere the Rings from Saturn
3. Empower Instruments to make Music
4. Empower Concensus to make Sometimes Design
5. Crouch intensely before the orifice of the Builders for the Houses to ooze forth
6. Slaver desperately at the orifice of the Programming for the Programs to ooze forth
